latestPosts.caption: There’s been a lot of jokes on here today, but in all seriousness a couple of months ago me and Marley opened up our relationship. I was hesitant at first to the idea, but when we met Theodore, I also fell in love with him. He has been such a loving partner to the both of us. A big reason we didn’t share with the world was well, because of who he is, a famous pop singer, a lot of people in Theodore’s past used him and he had major trust issues, but today he decided he wanted to share with the world; Us. So I hope you guys can accept Me, Marley, And Our Third…. Theodore.
